					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">What game are you trying to port? You'll run into a lot of issues if the game uses any timed code at all. Sprite 0-based status bars may be an issue too if you are not emulating the PPU.
<br />
<br />Also if you are not going to emulate the PPU you will likely need to rewrite fairly large chunks of the code.
<br />
<br />Sounds like an interesting project though.</div>

